headline: Western Digital Draws New Leveraged ETFs As Analysts Highlight Supply Story
summary: New leveraged ETFs tied to Western Digital were launched recently, giving traders amplified exposure to the stock. Several analysts issued upgrades on NasdaqGS:WDC, pointing to benefits from new technology and tight supply conditions in memory products. Western Digital, trading on NasdaqGS:WDC, has drawn fresh attention as its stock sits at $252.66, with very large 1 year and multi year returns.
